\c 24
\s UDavida uyekela uSawuli ukuthi aphile
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi uSawuli esebuyile ekulandeleni amaFilisti, bambikela besithi: Khangela, uDavida usenkangala yeEngedi\x + 23.28.\x*.
\v 2 USawuli wasethatha amadoda ayizinkulungwane ezintathu akhethiweyo kuIsrayeli wonke, wayadinga uDavida labantu bakhe phezu kwamadwala amagogo\x + 26.2. Nani 11.28.\x*.
\v 3 Wasefika ezibayeni zezimvu endleleni, lapho okwakulobhalu khona\x + Nani 32.16.\x*; uSawuli wasengena ukwembesa inyawo zakhe\x + Hlu. 3.24.\x*; uDavida labantu bakhe babehlezi-ke enhlangothini zobhalu.
\v 4 Abantu bakaDavida basebesithi kuye: Khangela, usuku iN\nd kosi\nd* ethi ngalo kuwe: Khangela, ngizanikela isitha sakho esandleni sakho, ukuthi wenze kuso njengokuhle emehlweni akho\x + 26.8.\x*. UDavida wasesukuma, wasika ensitha umphetho wesembatho uSawuli ayelaso.
\v 5 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokho inhliziyo kaDavida yamtshaya, ngenxa yokuthi wayesike umphetho wesembatho uSawuli ayelaso\x + 2 Sam. 24.10.\x*.
\v 6 Wasesithi ebantwini bakhe: Kakube khatshana lami ngeN\nd kosi\nd* ukuthi ngenze linto enkosini yami\x + 26.11.\x*, ogcotshiweyo weN\nd kosi\x + 24.10. 12.3.\x*\nd*, ukwelulela isandla sami kuye, ngoba engogcotshiweyo weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 7 UDavida wabanqanda abantu bakhe ngalawomazwi, kabavumelanga ukuthi bamvukele uSawuli\x + Hlab. 7.4. Mat. 5.44. Roma 12.17,19.\x*. USawuli wasesukuma waphuma ebhalwini, wahamba endleleni.
\v 8 Emva kwalokho uDavida laye wasukuma waphuma ebhalwini, wamemeza emva kukaSawuli esithi: Nkosi yami nkosi! Lapho uSawuli enyemukula, uDavida wakhothama ngobuso emhlabathini, wakhonza.
\p
\v 9 UDavida wasesithi kuSawuli: Ulalelelani amazwi abantu besithi: Khangela, uDavida udinga ukulinyazwa kwakho\x + Hlab. 141.6.\x*?
\v 10 Khangela, lamuhla amehlo akho abonile ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* ibikunikele lamuhla esandleni sami ebhalwini; njalo besithi ka\add ngi\add*kubulale\x + 24.4.\x*, kodwa \add nga\add*kuhawukela, ngathi: Kangiyikwelulela isandla sami enkosini yami, ngoba ingogcotshiweyo weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 11 Futhi-ke, baba, bona, yebo bona umphetho wesembatho sakho esandleni sami; ngoba ekusikeni kwami umphetho wesembatho sakho, lokuthi kangikubulalanga, yazi ubone ukuthi kakukho ububi lesiphambeko esandleni sami, njalo kangonanga kuwe, kanti wena uzingela umphefumulo wami ukuwuthatha\x + Gen. 45.20. Dute. 7.16. 13.9. 19.13,21.\x*.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayahlulele phakathi kwami lawe, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ingiphindiselele kuwe, kodwa isandla sami kasiyikumelana lawe\x + 24.15. Gen. 16.5. Hlu. 11.27. Jobe 5.8.\x*.
\v 13 Njengokutsho kwesaga sabendulo \add esithi\add*: Kwababi kuvela okubi; kodwa isandla sami kasiyikumelana lawe.
\v 14 Inkosi yakoIsrayeli iphume ukulandela bani? Uxotshana lobani? Emva kwenja efileyo\x + 2 Sam. 9.8. 2 Sam. 3.8.\x*, emva kwendwebundwebu eyodwa\x + 26.20.\x*!
\v 15 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* kayibe ngumahluleli, yahlulele phakathi kwami lawe\x + 24.12.\x*, ibone\x + 2 Lan. 24.22.\x*, ilumele udaba lwami\x + 25.39. Hlab. 35.1. 43.1. 119.154. Zaga 22.23. Jer. 50.34. 51.36. Lilo 3.58. Mika 7.9.\x*, ingikhulule esandleni sakho.
\p
\v 16 Kwasekusithi uDavida eseqedile ukukhuluma lamazwi kuSawuli, uSawuli wathi: Yilizwi lakho lelo yini, ndodana yami, Davida? USawuli wasephakamisa ilizwi lakhe, wakhala inyembezi\x + 26.17.\x*.
\v 17 Wasesithi kuDavida\x + 26.21.\x*: Ulungile kulami, ngoba wena ungivuze \add ngo\add*kuhle, kodwa mina ngikuvuze \add ngo\add*kubi.
\v 18 Wena-ke utshengisile lamuhla ukuthi wenze okuhle ngami, ngoba lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* ibinginikele esandleni sakho, kawungibulalanga\x + Gen. 38.26.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba nxa umuntu efica isitha sakhe, uzasiyekela sihambe ngendlela enhle yini? Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* ikuvuze \add ngo\add*kuhle ngokwenze kimi lamuhla.
\v 20 Manje-ke, khangela, ngiyazi ukuthi uzakuba yinkosi isibili, lokuthi umbuso wakoIsrayeli uzaqiniswa esandleni sakho\x + 23.17.\x*.
\v 21 Ngakho khathesi funga kimi ngeN\nd kosi\x + Gen. 21.23.\x*\nd* ukuthi kawuyikuyiquma inzalo yami emva kwami, lokuthi kawuyikulicitsha ibizo lami endlini kababa\x + 2 Sam. 21.7.\x*.
\v 22 UDavida wasefunga kuSawuli, loSawuli waya endlini yakhe, kodwa uDavida labantu bakhe benyukela enqabeni\x + 23.29.\x*.